export const activityError = {
    dateTimeEmptyError: "Date and Time must not be empty",
    distanceEmptyError: "Distance must not be empty",
    distanceNegativeError: "Distance must not be negative",
    durationEmptyError: "Duration must not be empty",
    durationFormatError: "Duration format must be Minutes:Seconds",
    durationNegativeError: "Duration must not be negative",
    activityTypeEmptyError: "Activity type must not be empty",
    imageSizeError: "Image size must be less than 5MB",
    imageFileTypeError: "Image type must be jpg or png",
};
